{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_MAIN.gif?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TAGLINE3.png?t=1736324700\" />World War One expands to the mountains of the Italian Front - beautiful but deadly in equal measure. Take part in key offensives of the Great War, from the Sixth Battle of the Isonzo to the Strafexpedition, and lead your team to victory among the scenic landscapes and peaks of Northern Italy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Isonzo is a realistic tactical multiplayer FPS crafted by BlackMill Games, known for their critically acclaimed authentic WW1 wargames such as Verdun and Tannenberg. Immerse yourself in faithful recreations of historical battles with intense 48-player matches, testing your tactical skills and mastery of Alpine warfare. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_1_master-high-altitude-combat.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_Combat.gif?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decide your path to victory: whether you\u2019re leading the offensive with grenades or using mountain trails to flank enemy positions, you have options. Dive into combat or take a supporting role cutting barbed wire and crewing heavy machine guns and mortars. Thanks to a unique flare gun system, mark targets for artillery strikes or biplane flybys, before charging in to finish the job at close quarters with bayonets or trench clubs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_2_become-the-specialist-your-team-needs.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_Specialist.gif?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from six distinct classes and build your loadout from a selection of 50+ iconic WW1 weapons, along with historically accurate equipment and perks specific to each class. Play as a Marksman to pick off soldiers from afar, storm enemy lines with the Assault class, issue tactical orders as an Officer, and much more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/2.1._Classes.png?t=1736324700\" />After choosing a class, make it your own by picking from a large variety of role-appropriate uniforms, accessories and headgear. As a finishing touch, you can even pick your mustache from several famous wartime styles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_3_fight-across-the-italian-alps.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/3._GIF_Maps.gif?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From hillside fortresses to mountain trenches and city streets, fight through varied Alpine landscapes inspired by historical battles. Learn the lay of the land to maintain cover and surprise your enemies - or go a step further to shape a dynamic battlefield by placing sandbags, barbed wire and ammo crates. Trench periscopes and sniper shields offer even more tactical options, but beware of poisonous gas attacks and artillery barrages! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_4_experience-the-great-war.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_WW1.gif?t=1736324700\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Taking inspiration from the years-long struggle for control of the Alps during World War One, Isonzo brings the authenticity of the conflict to all players. Everything is recreated based on research and field trips, from sound effects, weapons and uniforms down to the houses, vineyards and trenches you\u2019ll be fighting over. Choose your side and immerse yourself in History!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/overview_adamello_steam.png?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ww1series_steam_packageheader_628x205_storetext.png?t=1736324700\" />Enlist for more First World War action with the other standalone titles in the WW1 Game Series: Tannenberg and Verdun. Experience trench warfare on the Western Front in Verdun, or maneuver for control of key sectors in Tannenberg on the Eastern Front. Choose from a range of squads from across the war, as they fight for control of the ever-changing frontlines.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Can I Go Home Now?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/50382b065c959a844727f283f9707719acf4ef15.jpg"},{"name":"Avanti Savoia!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/0d069c57d5107fa91a7535cb4e787f9503c14253.jpg"},{"name":"Donatello","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/a4a1757be8658e75a23aa25d70a965d0bdd77512.jpg"},{"name":"Silver Lining","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/d0c8e9bcd322ad2f1ce99261d403aa64150f0cb9.jpg"},{"name":"Aurelio Baruzzi","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/811262cef4f73f8a9000f4aaa840a3b65d3fd391.jpg"},{"name":"Cercatore d'Oro","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/a4a1757be8658e75a23aa25d70a965d0bdd77512.jpg"},{"name":"Veni Vidi Vici","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/c86b7767a6037e979f4df68c1905ce6468cd82ae.jpg"},{"name":"Conrad von Hotzensocks","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/b4fd670585d26fc399fc8b94bdf3b0c130d750bc.jpg"},{"name":"Peak Performance","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/b3828e5c018507d3129548fda899b2e2c4100fb2.jpg"},{"name":"The Lion of the Isonzo","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1556790/eaea7bbc0083cc28350eb4eb84a9a155bdb8f00a.jpg"}],"total":48},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736324700","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/page.bg.jpg?t=1736324700","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736324700","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736324700","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":36},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Trading Cards","id":29},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"This Game may contain content not appropriate for all ages, or may not be appropriate for viewing at work: Frequent Violence or Gore, General Mature Content.\r\nGore and blood can be disabled completely with an in-game setting.\r\n"},"detailed_description":"<h1>FREE ADAMELLO EXPANSION</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/Adamello_Art_Description.png?t=1736324700\" />With the free Adamello expansion, fight on a new battlefield 3,000+ metres high in the Adamello-Presanella Alps! Endure fierce, icy winds and trek through thick snow as you fight for control of the Presena peak, and wield two new weapons: the Artillery Luger and the Petardo Offensivo 'P.O' grenade. </p></p><br><h1>PC Editions Overview</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/PC_Editions_Overview__Steam_.png?t=1736324700\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_MAIN.gif?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TAGLINE3.png?t=1736324700\" />World War One expands to the mountains of the Italian Front - beautiful but deadly in equal measure. Take part in key offensives of the Great War, from the Sixth Battle of the Isonzo to the Strafexpedition, and lead your team to victory among the scenic landscapes and peaks of Northern Italy. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Isonzo is a realistic tactical multiplayer FPS crafted by BlackMill Games, known for their critically acclaimed authentic WW1 wargames such as Verdun and Tannenberg. Immerse yourself in faithful recreations of historical battles with intense 48-player matches, testing your tactical skills and mastery of Alpine warfare. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_1_master-high-altitude-combat.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_Combat.gif?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decide your path to victory: whether you\u2019re leading the offensive with grenades or using mountain trails to flank enemy positions, you have options. Dive into combat or take a supporting role cutting barbed wire and crewing heavy machine guns and mortars. Thanks to a unique flare gun system, mark targets for artillery strikes or biplane flybys, before charging in to finish the job at close quarters with bayonets or trench clubs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_2_become-the-specialist-your-team-needs.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_Specialist.gif?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from six distinct classes and build your loadout from a selection of 50+ iconic WW1 weapons, along with historically accurate equipment and perks specific to each class. Play as a Marksman to pick off soldiers from afar, storm enemy lines with the Assault class, issue tactical orders as an Officer, and much more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/2.1._Classes.png?t=1736324700\" />After choosing a class, make it your own by picking from a large variety of role-appropriate uniforms, accessories and headgear. As a finishing touch, you can even pick your mustache from several famous wartime styles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_3_fight-across-the-italian-alps.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/3._GIF_Maps.gif?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From hillside fortresses to mountain trenches and city streets, fight through varied Alpine landscapes inspired by historical battles. Learn the lay of the land to maintain cover and surprise your enemies - or go a step further to shape a dynamic battlefield by placing sandbags, barbed wire and ammo crates. Trench periscopes and sniper shields offer even more tactical options, but beware of poisonous gas attacks and artillery barrages! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ISONZO_STEAM_TITRE_4_experience-the-great-war.png?t=1736324700\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/GIF_WW1.gif?t=1736324700\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Taking inspiration from the years-long struggle for control of the Alps during World War One, Isonzo brings the authenticity of the conflict to all players. Everything is recreated based on research and field trips, from sound effects, weapons and uniforms down to the houses, vineyards and trenches you\u2019ll be fighting over. Choose your side and immerse yourself in History!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/overview_adamello_steam.png?t=1736324700\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/extras/ww1series_steam_packageheader_628x205_storetext.png?t=1736324700\" />Enlist for more First World War action with the other standalone titles in the WW1 Game Series: Tannenberg and Verdun. Experience trench warfare on the Western Front in Verdun, or maneuver for control of key sectors in Tannenberg on the Eastern Front. Choose from a range of squads from across the war, as they fight for control of the ever-changing frontlines.</p>","developers":["BlackMill Games"],"dlc":[2719550,2753070,2542150,2542160,2719540,2214670,2214671,2197970,2078340,1815510,1815511,1815512,1815513],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Massively Multiplayer","id":"29"},{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556790/header.jpg?t=1736324700","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"\u00a9 Copyright 2024 BlackMill Games. All rights reserved.","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i5-4670K, AMD Ryzen 5 1400<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 8 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GeForce GTX 970, AMD Radeon R9 290, 4GB VRAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 30 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i7-6700K, AMD Ryzen 5 3600<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 16 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> GeForce GTX 1070, AMD Radeon RX 580, 8GB VRAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 30 GB available space</li></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Catalina 10.15.4 or newer<br></li><li><strong>Processor